# Fix missing `updateFile` in [useFileManager](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx#145-203)

The [useFileManager](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx#145-203) hook in [CustomFilePicker.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx) is missing the `updateFile` method, which is required by [CreatePost.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/pages/CreatePost.tsx) to handle cropped images.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name]

#### [MODIFY] [CustomFilePicker.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx)

1.  Add `updateFile` to the [useFileManager](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx#145-203) hook.
2.  Ensure `updateFile` revokes the old object URL if it's being replaced.
3.  Include `updateFile` in the memoized return object.

